sentence: The Transactions include the filing of a Second Amended and Restated Certificate of Incorporation of the Issuer filed as Exhibit 3.1 to the Form 8-K of the Issuer, dated March 1, 2010 (the Second Amended Charter) with the Secretary of State of the State of Delaware to authorize additional shares of common stock and convertible preferred stock in amounts sufficient for the proposed issuance of common stock and convertible preferred stock and for the ultimate conversion of such convertible preferred stock into common stock.
